# GitHub API Configuration (Optional - for GitHub contribution graph only)
#
# PRODUCTION: Token is stored in GitHub Actions secrets (no setup needed)
#
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ONLY: To test the GitHub contribution graph locally:
# 1. Create a token at https://github.com/settings/tokens
# 2. Select ONLY the 'read:user' scope (read-only access)
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and add your token:
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GITHUB_TOKEN=your_token_here
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GITHUB_USERNAME=richfergus
#
# Note: .env.local is gitignored and won't be committed
